<div class="dp-settings-header">
    <div><h2 class="mb-1">Digital product experience</h2><p class="text-muted mb-0">Design the public shop, passwordless sign-in, cart, payment handoff, confirmation, and customer purchase library. The fullscreen editor previews every state before you save.</p></div>
    <div class="dp-settings-actions"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="open-dp-editor">Open live editor</button>@if(previewStoreUrl is not null){<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="@previewStoreUrl" target="_blank">View shop</a>}<a class="btn btn-secondary" asp-action="Index" asp-route-storeId="@storeId">Back</a></div>
</div>
<partial name="_StatusMessage" />
<form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" asp-action="SaveSettings" asp-route-storeId="@storeId" id="dp-settings-form" data-loading-title="Saving storefront…">
    <div asp-validation-summary="All" class="text-danger"></div>
    <input asp-for="CustomerAccountsEnabled" type="hidden" value="true">
    <input asp-for="HeroImageUrl" type="hidden"><input asp-for="HeroEyebrow" type="hidden"><input asp-for="HeroHeadline" type="hidden"><input asp-for="HeroSubheadline" type="hidden"><input asp-for="BrandPanelWidth" type="hidden">
    <input type="hidden" name="heroSlidesJson" id="heroSlidesJson" value="@heroSlidesJson"><input type="hidden" name="categoriesJson" id="categoriesJson" value="@categoriesJson">
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-12"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card dp-domain-guide" aria-labelledby="dp-domain-guide-title">
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-start justify-content-between gap-3"><div><h4 id="dp-domain-guide-title">Use your own domain</h4><p class="text-muted mb-0">Publish this storefront through a branded hostname while BTCPay keeps payment and protected delivery on your server.</p></div><span class="badge bg-info text-dark">Server administrator required</span></div>
            <div class="row g-3 mt-1">
                <div class="col-lg-6"><div class="h-100 rounded border p-3"><div class="small text-uppercase fw-semibold text-muted mb-2">Current canonical URL</div>@if(canonicalStoreUrl is not null){<a class="dp-domain-current font-monospace" href="@canonicalStoreUrl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@canonicalStoreUrl</a>}else{<code class="dp-domain-current">/stores/@storeId/downloads</code>}<p class="small text-muted mb-0 mt-2">After a branded hostname is connected, the supported route keeps the same <code>/stores/&lt;storeId&gt;/downloads</code> path.</p></div></div>
                <div class="col-lg-6"><div class="h-100 rounded border p-3"><div class="small text-uppercase fw-semibold text-muted mb-2">Recommended setup</div><p class="mb-2">Use a dedicated hostname such as <code>shop.example.com</code>. Configure DNS first, then have the BTCPay server administrator enable that hostname and HTTPS.</p><p class="small text-muted mb-0">A CNAME alone is insufficient: the receiving reverse proxy must accept the hostname and present a valid TLS certificate.</p></div></div>
            </div>
            <details class="dp-domain-step mt-3">
                <summary>Server command template for an official BTCPay Docker deployment</summary>
                <ol class="mb-3 ps-3">
                    <li class="mb-2">Create an A/AAAA record to the BTCPay server IP, or a CNAME to its public hostname. Wait until the new hostname resolves correctly.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Confirm ports 80 and 443 reach BTCPay. Then connect over SSH as the server administrator.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Set <code>BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS</code> to the complete comma-separated list, including every existing additional hostname, and rerun setup:</li>
                </ol>
                <pre><code># Replace both placeholders. Run as root from the btcpayserver-docker directory.
export BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS="&lt;your-new-host&gt;,&lt;all-existing-additional-hosts&gt;"
. ./btcpay-setup.sh -i</code></pre>
                <p class="alert alert-warning small mb-0"><strong>DNS must work before setup.</strong> An unresolved or incorrectly configured additional hostname can prevent Let's Encrypt renewal for every hostname, including the main BTCPay domain.</p>
                <p class="small text-muted mt-2 mb-0"><code>BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS</code> aliases the whole BTCPay Server, not only this store. Other BTCPay and store-scoped public routes remain reachable on that hostname; do not treat it as domain-to-store isolation.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="dp-domain-step mt-3">
                <summary>About a clean <code>/downloads</code> URL or an existing website</summary>
                <p>The hostname setup above makes <code>https://shop.example.com/stores/&lt;storeId&gt;/downloads</code> available. DNS and <code>BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS</code> do not remove the store-scoped route.</p>
                <p>A clean <code>https://shop.example.com/downloads</code> address needs a host-to-store short-route implementation in the plugin, or a correctly configured external reverse proxy that rewrites the storefront and every related asset, checkout, callback, and protected-delivery route. Digital Products is not currently registered as a BTCPay App, so Server Settings → Policies cannot map it to a clean root route.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">If <code>example.com</code> already hosts another website, that website's reverse proxy or CDN must own the path routing. This cannot be configured from inside the BTCPay plugin; a dedicated subdomain is safer.</p>
            </details>
            <div class="dp-domain-links small mt-3">
                <a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/Docker/#environment-variables" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docker additional-host settings</a>
                <a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/FAQ/Apps/#how-to-map-a-domain-name-to-an-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BTCPay App mapping background</a>
                <a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/FAQ/Deployment/#can-i-use-an-existing-nginx-server-as-a-reverse-proxy-with-ssl-termination" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reverse proxy and TLS guide</a>
            </div>
        </section></div>
        <div class="col-xl-6"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card"><h4>Brand &amp; storefront</h4><p class="text-muted">Core identity and catalog copy. Hero slides, uploads, links, and categories are managed in the live editor.</p>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="StorefrontTitle" class="form-label">Storefront name</label><input asp-for="StorefrontTitle" class="form-control"></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="StorefrontAnnouncement" class="form-label">Announcement bar</label><input asp-for="StorefrontAnnouncement" class="form-control"><div class="form-text">Leave blank to hide the bar.</div></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="StorefrontDescription" class="form-label">Storefront description</label><textarea asp-for="StorefrontDescription" class="form-control" rows="2"></textarea></div>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-7 form-group"><label asp-for="LogoUrl" class="form-label">Logo URL</label><input asp-for="LogoUrl" class="form-control" placeholder="https://… or upload in live editor"></div><div class="col-md-5 form-group"><label asp-for="HeroAutoAdvanceSeconds" class="form-label">Slide timing (seconds)</label><input asp-for="HeroAutoAdvanceSeconds" class="form-control"><div class="form-text">Set 0 to disable.</div></div></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="FaviconUrl" class="form-label">Favicon URL</label><input asp-for="FaviconUrl" class="form-control" placeholder="https://… or upload in live editor"><div class="form-text">Browser-tab icon for every public storefront, checkout, and purchase page. Use an HTTP(S) image URL or upload a PNG or ICO file in the live editor; leave blank to emit no custom favicon.</div></div>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="LogoWidth" class="form-label">Logo width (px)</label><input asp-for="LogoWidth" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="LogoHeight" class="form-label">Logo height (px)</label><input asp-for="LogoHeight" class="form-control"></div></div>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="CatalogTitle" class="form-label">Catalog title</label><input asp-for="CatalogTitle" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="CatalogSubtitle" class="form-label">Catalog subtitle</label><input asp-for="CatalogSubtitle" class="form-control"></div></div>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="FontStyle" class="form-label">Typeface style</label><select asp-for="FontStyle" asp-items="Html.GetEnumSelectList<DigitalStoreFontStyle>()" class="form-select"></select></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="Currency" class="form-label"></label><input asp-for="Currency" class="form-control"></div></div>
            <div class="row g-3"><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="AccentColor" class="form-label">Accent</label><input asp-for="AccentColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="AccentTextColor" class="form-label">Button text</label><input asp-for="AccentTextColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="BrandTextColor" class="form-label">Hero text</label><input asp-for="BrandTextColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="PageBackgroundColor" class="form-label">Page</label><input asp-for="PageBackgroundColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="SurfaceColor" class="form-label">Cards</label><input asp-for="SurfaceColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="TextColor" class="form-label">Text</label><input asp-for="TextColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="MutedColor" class="form-label">Muted text</label><input asp-for="MutedColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div><div class="col-6 col-md-4"><label asp-for="SoftColor" class="form-label">Soft surface</label><input asp-for="SoftColor" type="color" class="form-control form-control-color w-100"></div></div>
        </section></div>
        <div class="col-xl-6"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card"><h4>Customer access &amp; completion</h4><p class="text-muted">Passwordless access, purchase library, confirmation, and public policies.</p>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="LoginCodeMinutes" class="form-label">Login code lifetime (minutes)</label><input asp-for="LoginCodeMinutes" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="CustomerSessionHours" class="form-label">Customer session (hours)</label><input asp-for="CustomerSessionHours" class="form-control"></div></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="LibraryTitle" class="form-label">Library title</label><input asp-for="LibraryTitle" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="LibrarySubtitle" class="form-label">Library subtitle</label><textarea asp-for="LibrarySubtitle" class="form-control" rows="2"></textarea></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="ConfirmationTitle" class="form-label">Confirmation title</label><input asp-for="ConfirmationTitle" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="ConfirmationMessage" class="form-label">Confirmation message</label><textarea asp-for="ConfirmationMessage" class="form-control" rows="2"></textarea></div>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="PrivacyUrl" class="form-label">Privacy URL</label><input asp-for="PrivacyUrl" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="TermsUrl" class="form-label">Terms URL</label><input asp-for="TermsUrl" class="form-control"></div></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="FooterText" class="form-label">Footer text</label><textarea asp-for="FooterText" class="form-control" rows="2"></textarea></div>
            <h5 class="mt-4">Passwordless sign-in email</h5><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="LoginEmailSubject" class="form-label">Subject</label><input asp-for="LoginEmailSubject" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="LoginEmailHtml" class="form-label">HTML template</label><textarea asp-for="LoginEmailHtml" rows="6" class="form-control font-monospace"></textarea><div class="form-text">Available: {StoreName}, {Code}, {Minutes}</div></div>
            <h5 class="mt-4">Purchase email</h5><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="PurchaseEmailSubject" class="form-label">Subject</label><input asp-for="PurchaseEmailSubject" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="PurchaseEmailHtml" class="form-label">HTML template</label><textarea asp-for="PurchaseEmailHtml" rows="6" class="form-control font-monospace"></textarea><div class="form-text">Available: {StoreName}, {PurchaseUrl}, {LibraryUrl}</div></div>
        </section></div>
        <div class="col-xl-6"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card"><h4>Google analytics &amp; commerce events</h4><p class="text-muted">Connect one Google provider. The plugin emits normalized GA4 ecommerce events without customer email, license keys, access tokens, or other purchase PII.</p>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="AnalyticsProvider" class="form-label">Provider</label><select asp-for="AnalyticsProvider" asp-items="Html.GetEnumSelectList<AnalyticsProvider>()" class="form-select"></select><div class="form-text">Choose either GTM or direct GA4 to avoid duplicate reporting. Disabled still keeps the local <code>dataLayer</code> contract available for testing or an externally injected container.</div></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="form-label">Google Tag Manager container ID</label><input asp-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="form-control font-monospace" placeholder="GTM-ABC123" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"><span asp-validation-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="text-danger"></span><div class="form-text">A merchant-controlled GTM container can read the browser URL. On protected checkout and sign-in routes, trigger tags from the plugin's <code>page_view</code> event and map its safe <code>page_location</code>/<code>page_path</code>; do not use an automatic All Pages trigger or the built-in Page URL variable.</div></div>
            <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="form-label">Google Analytics 4 measurement ID</label><input asp-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="form-control font-monospace" placeholder="G-ABC123DEF4" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"><span asp-validation-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="text-danger"></span></div>
            <div class="form-check mb-2"><input asp-for="RequireAnalyticsConsent" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="RequireAnalyticsConsent" class="form-check-label">Require visitor consent before loading Google scripts</label></div>
            <div class="form-check mb-3"><input asp-for="RespectDoNotTrack" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="RespectDoNotTrack" class="form-check-label">Respect browser Do Not Track</label></div>
            <div class="rounded border p-3 small text-muted"><strong class="text-body">Events included</strong><br><code>view_item_list</code>, <code>select_item</code>, <code>view_item</code>, <code>add_to_cart</code>, <code>remove_from_cart</code>, <code>view_cart</code>, <code>begin_checkout</code>, <code>add_payment_info</code>, and <code>purchase</code>. Purchase uses best-effort browser deduplication and a stable one-way transaction ID.</div>
        </section></div>
        <div class="col-xl-6"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card"><h4>Download protection &amp; storage</h4><p class="text-muted">Protected link lifetime, local/S3 delivery, and authenticated custom URLs.</p>
            <div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="DefaultDownloadLimit" class="form-label">Default download limit</label><input asp-for="DefaultDownloadLimit" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="DefaultLinkHours" class="form-label">Default link lifetime (hours)</label><input asp-for="DefaultLinkHours" class="form-control"></div></div>
            <div class="form-check mb-2"><input asp-for="LockToFirstIp" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="LockToFirstIp" class="form-check-label">Lock a link to the first downloader IP</label></div><div class="form-check mb-3"><input asp-for="DeliverOnProcessing" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="DeliverOnProcessing" class="form-check-label">Deliver at Processing (higher payment risk)</label></div>
            <h5>S3-compatible storage</h5><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="S3Endpoint" class="form-label">Endpoint</label><input asp-for="S3Endpoint" class="form-control"></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="S3Region" class="form-label">Region</label><input asp-for="S3Region" class="form-control"></div><div class="col-md-6 form-group"><label asp-for="S3Bucket" class="form-label">Bucket</label><input asp-for="S3Bucket" class="form-control"></div></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="S3AccessKey" class="form-label">Access key</label><input asp-for="S3AccessKey" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Secret key</label><input type="password" name="s3SecretKey" autocomplete="new-password" class="form-control" placeholder="Leave blank to keep existing"></div>
            <h5 class="mt-4">Custom URL authentication</h5><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="RemoteAuthorizationHeader" class="form-label">Header name</label><input asp-for="RemoteAuthorizationHeader" class="form-control" placeholder="Authorization"></div><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">Header value</label><input type="password" name="remoteAuthorizationValue" autocomplete="new-password" class="form-control" placeholder="Bearer … (leave blank to keep)"></div>
        </section></div>
        <div class="col-xl-6"><section class="bg-tile rounded p-4 dp-settings-card"><h4>Legacy delivery</h4><p class="text-muted">Compatibility email for older single-item purchase links.</p>
            <div class="form-check mb-3"><input asp-for="EmailDeliveryEnabled" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="EmailDeliveryEnabled" class="form-check-label">Send delivery email through BTCPay store SMTP</label></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="EmailSubject" class="form-label">Legacy email subject</label><input asp-for="EmailSubject" class="form-control"></div><div class="form-group"><label asp-for="EmailHtml" class="form-label">Legacy HTML template</label><textarea asp-for="EmailHtml" rows="7" class="form-control font-monospace"></textarea><div class="form-text">Available: {StoreName}, {ProductName}, {DownloadUrl}, {ExpiresAt}</div></div>
        </section></div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary mt-4" id="dp-settings-submit">Save settings</button>
</form>

<dialog class="dp-editor-dialog" id="dp-editor" aria-label="Live digital shop editor">
    <div class="dp-editor-shell">
        <header class="dp-editor-topbar">
            <div class="dp-editor-top-left">
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-icon-button dp-editor-back" id="close-dp-editor" aria-label="Close editor" title="Close editor"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#back"></use></svg></button>
                <div class="dp-editor-mode-switcher" aria-label="Editor modes">
                    <button type="button" class="dp-editor-mode-button is-active" data-editor-mode="sections" aria-label="Sections" title="Sections"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#actions-drag"></use></svg></button>
                    <button type="button" class="dp-editor-mode-button" data-editor-mode="theme" aria-label="Theme" title="Theme"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#themes-light"></use></svg></button>
                    <button type="button" class="dp-editor-mode-button" data-editor-mode="pages" aria-label="Page content" title="Page content"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#forms-text"></use></svg></button>
                    <button type="button" class="dp-editor-mode-button" data-editor-mode="header" aria-label="Header" title="Header"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#nav-store"></use></svg></button>
                    <button type="button" class="dp-editor-mode-button" data-editor-mode="footer" aria-label="Footer" title="Footer"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#nav-menu"></use></svg></button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dp-editor-top-center">
                <label class="dp-editor-page-control"><span>Page</span><select id="dp-editor-page" aria-label="Preview page"><option value="shop">Shop homepage</option><option value="product">Product detail</option><option value="cart">Shopping cart</option><option value="login">Sign in</option><option value="payment">Payment</option><option value="success">Confirmation</option><option value="library">Purchase library</option></select></label>
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-add-button" id="dp-editor-add"><svg class="dp-editor-icon dp-editor-icon-sm"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#actions-add"></use></svg><span>Add slide</span></button>
            </div>
            <div class="dp-editor-top-right">
                <div class="dp-editor-status" id="dp-editor-status"><svg class="dp-editor-icon dp-editor-icon-sm"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#checkmark"></use></svg><span>Published</span><i class="dp-editor-status-dot"></i><span data-status-copy>Saved</span></div>
                <div class="dp-editor-device-switcher"><button type="button" class="is-active" data-preview-device="desktop" aria-label="Desktop preview" title="Desktop preview"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#nav-dashboard"></use></svg></button><button type="button" data-preview-device="mobile" aria-label="Mobile preview" title="Mobile preview"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#nav-mobile-menu"></use></svg></button></div>
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-icon-button" id="dp-editor-undo" aria-label="Undo" title="Undo (Cmd/Ctrl+Z)" disabled><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#caret-left"></use></svg></button>
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-icon-button" id="dp-editor-redo" aria-label="Redo" title="Redo (Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+Z)" disabled><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#caret-right"></use></svg></button>
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-icon-button" data-select-type="general" aria-label="General settings" title="General settings"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#settings"></use></svg></button>
                <button type="button" class="dp-editor-save" id="save-dp-editor"><svg class="dp-editor-icon dp-editor-icon-sm"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#done"></use></svg><span>Save</span></button>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="dp-editor-layout">
            <aside class="dp-editor-sidebar">
                <div class="dp-editor-sidebar-head"><strong id="dp-editor-sidebar-title">Shop homepage</strong><span class="small text-muted">Page</span></div>
                <div class="dp-editor-sidebar-body" id="dp-editor-sidebar-body"></div>
            </aside>
            <main class="dp-editor-canvas">
                <div class="dp-editor-frame-stage"><div class="dp-editor-frame-wrap" id="dp-editor-frame-wrap"><iframe class="dp-editor-frame" id="dp-editor-frame" title="Digital shop preview"></iframe></div></div>
            </main>
            <aside class="dp-editor-inspector">
                <div class="dp-editor-inspector-head"><strong id="dp-editor-inspector-title">Section settings</strong><button type="button" class="dp-editor-icon-button" data-select-type="general" aria-label="General settings"><svg class="dp-editor-icon"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#settings"></use></svg></button></div>
                <div class="dp-editor-inspector-content" id="dp-editor-inspector-content"></div>
            </aside>
        </div>
        <div id="dp-editor-upload-bin" hidden></div>
    </div>
</dialog>
<script type="application/json" id="dp-slides-data">@Html.Raw(heroSlidesJson)</script>
<script type="application/json" id="dp-categories-data">@Html.Raw(categoriesJson)</script>
<script type="application/json" id="dp-catalog-data">@Html.Raw(catalogJson)</script>
<script>
(()=>{
    const dialog=document.getElementById('dp-editor');
    const form=document.getElementById('dp-settings-form');
    const frame=document.getElementById('dp-editor-frame');
    const frameWrap=document.getElementById('dp-editor-frame-wrap');
    const sidebar=document.getElementById('dp-editor-sidebar-body');
    const inspector=document.getElementById('dp-editor-inspector-content');
    const inspectorTitle=document.getElementById('dp-editor-inspector-title');
    const pageSelect=document.getElementById('dp-editor-page');
    const addButton=document.getElementById('dp-editor-add');
    const status=document.getElementById('dp-editor-status');
    const saveButton=document.getElementById('save-dp-editor');
    const undoButton=document.getElementById('dp-editor-undo');
    const redoButton=document.getElementById('dp-editor-redo');
    const slidesField=document.getElementById('heroSlidesJson');
    const categoriesField=document.getElementById('categoriesJson');
    const uploadBin=document.getElementById('dp-editor-upload-bin');
    const source=id=>document.getElementById(id);
    const value=id=>source(id)?.value||'';
    const escapeHtml=text=>String(text??'').replace(/[&<>"']/g,char=>({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;',"'":'&#39;'}[char]));
    const escapeAttribute=escapeHtml;
    const clone=value=>JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(value));
    const color=(id,fallback)=>/^#[0-9a-f]{6}$/i.test(value(id))?value(id):fallback;
    const slugify=text=>String(text||'category').toLowerCase().trim().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g,'-').replace(/^-|-$/g,'').slice(0,80)||'category';
    const uid=()=>crypto.randomUUID().replaceAll('-','');
    const publicUrl=input=>{const raw=String(input||'').trim();if(raw.startsWith('/')&&!raw.startsWith('//'))return location.origin+raw;try{const parsed=new URL(raw);return /^https?:$/.test(parsed.protocol)?parsed.href:''}catch{return''}};
    const icon=name=>`<svg class="dp-editor-icon dp-editor-icon-sm"><use href="/img/icon-sprite.svg#${name}"></use></svg>`;
    const trackedFields=['StorefrontTitle','StorefrontAnnouncement','StorefrontDescription','LogoUrl','FaviconUrl','LogoWidth','LogoHeight','HeroAutoAdvanceSeconds','CatalogTitle','CatalogSubtitle','FontStyle','Currency','AccentColor','AccentTextColor','BrandTextColor','PageBackgroundColor','SurfaceColor','TextColor','MutedColor','SoftColor','LibraryTitle','LibrarySubtitle','ConfirmationTitle','ConfirmationMessage','PrivacyUrl','TermsUrl','FooterText','LoginCodeMinutes','CustomerSessionHours','LoginEmailSubject','LoginEmailHtml','PurchaseEmailSubject','PurchaseEmailHtml'];
    let slides=JSON.parse(document.getElementById('dp-slides-data').textContent||'[]');
    const parsedCategories=JSON.parse(document.getElementById('dp-categories-data').textContent||'[]');
    const categorySlugs=new Set();
    let categories=parsedCategories.filter(category=>{
        const key=String(category.slug||'').trim().toLowerCase();
        if(!key||categorySlugs.has(key))return false;
        categorySlugs.add(key);
        return true;
    });
    const products=JSON.parse(document.getElementById('dp-catalog-data').textContent||'[]');
    let page='shop';
    let device='desktop';
    let mode='sections';
    let selected={type:'hero',index:0};
    let activeSlide=0;
    let logoPreview='';
    const slidePreviews={};
    let history=[];
    let future=[];
    let savedSignature='';
    let uploadsDirty=false;
    let editStartSnapshot=null;
    let draggedLayer=null;
    let pendingPreviewScroll=0;
    const storageKey='makepay:digital-products-editor:@storeId';

    const serialize=()=>{
        slidesField.value=JSON.stringify(slides);
        categoriesField.value=JSON.stringify(categories);
        const primary=slides.find(slide=>slide.visible)??slides[0];
        if(primary){source('HeroEyebrow').value=primary.eyebrow||'';source('HeroHeadline').value=primary.headline||'';source('HeroSubheadline').value=primary.supportingCopy||'';source('HeroImageUrl').value=primary.imageUrl||''}
    };
    const capture=()=>({fields:Object.fromEntries(trackedFields.map(id=>{const field=source(id);return[id,field?.type==='checkbox'?field.checked:field?.value||'']})),slides:clone(slides),categories:clone(categories)});
    const signature=snapshot=>JSON.stringify(snapshot);
    const applySnapshot=snapshot=>{Object.entries(snapshot.fields||{}).forEach(([id,next])=>{const field=source(id);if(field){if(field.type==='checkbox')field.checked=Boolean(next);else field.value=next}});slides=clone(snapshot.slides||[]);categories=clone(snapshot.categories||[]);activeSlide=Math.max(0,Math.min(activeSlide,slides.length-1));serialize();renderAll()};
    const pushHistory=before=>{if(!before||signature(before)===signature(capture()))return;history=[...history,before].slice(-80);future=[];updateStatus()};
    const mutate=action=>{const before=capture();action();serialize();pushHistory(before);renderAll()};
    const isDirty=()=>signature(capture())!==savedSignature||uploadsDirty;
    const updateStatus=()=>{const dirty=isDirty();status.classList.toggle('is-dirty',dirty);status.querySelector('[data-status-copy]').textContent=dirty?'Unsaved changes':'Saved';saveButton.disabled=!dirty;undoButton.disabled=history.length===0;redoButton.disabled=future.length===0};
    const undo=()=>{const previous=history.pop();if(!previous)return;future.unshift(capture());applySnapshot(previous);updateStatus()};
    const redo=()=>{const next=future.shift();if(!next)return;history.push(capture());applySnapshot(next);updateStatus()};
    const selectedClass=(type,index=null)=>selected.type===type&&(index===null||Number(selected.index)===Number(index))?' editor-selected':'';
    const select=(type,index=null)=>{const previousSlide=activeSlide;selected={type,index};if(type==='slide'&&Number.isInteger(Number(index)))activeSlide=Number(index);if(type==='general')mode='theme';else if(type==='header')mode='header';else if(type==='footer')mode='footer';else if(['product','cart','login','payment','success','library'].includes(type))mode='pages';else mode='sections';renderSidebar();renderInspector(false);updateTopbar();updateStatus();if(type==='slide'&&activeSlide!==previousSlide)renderPreview(true);else updatePreviewSelection();persistUiState()};
    const pageLabels={shop:'Shop homepage',product:'Product detail',cart:'Shopping cart',login:'Sign in',payment:'Payment',success:'Confirmation',library:'Purchase library'};
    const categoryMatches=(category,product)=>{
        const rule=Number(category.rule);
        if(rule===1)return product.kind==='Download'&&(!product.productType||product.productType==='FileDownload');
        if(rule===2)return product.kind==='License';
        if(rule===3)return product.kind==='Download'&&product.productType==='PdfEbook';
        if(rule===4)return product.kind==='Download'&&product.productType==='Audio';
        if(rule===5)return product.kind==='Download'&&product.productType==='Video';
        if(rule===6)return product.kind==='Download'&&product.productType==='PhotosArt';
        return (category.productReferences||[]).includes(product.reference);
    };
    const layerButton=(type,label,sub,index=null,options={})=>`<div class="dp-editor-layer${selectedClass(type,index)}" draggable="${options.draggable?'true':'false'}" data-layer-type="${type}" ${index===null?'':`data-layer-index="${index}"`}><span class="dp-editor-layer-grip">${icon(options.draggable?'actions-drag':options.icon||'block')}</span><button type="button" class="dp-editor-layer-main" data-select-type="${type}" ${index===null?'':`data-select-index="${index}"`}><strong>${escapeHtml(label)}</strong><span>${escapeHtml(sub)}</span></button><div class="dp-editor-layer-actions">${options.visibility?`<button type="button" class="dp-editor-layer-icon" data-layer-visibility="${type}" data-layer-index="${index}" aria-label="${options.visible?'Hide':'Show'}">${icon(options.visible?'actions-show':'actions-hide')}</button>`:''}${options.draggable?`<button type="button" class="dp-editor-layer-icon" data-layer-move="up" data-layer-type="${type}" data-layer-index="${index}" aria-label="Move up">${icon('caret-up')}</button><button type="button" class="dp-editor-layer-icon" data-layer-move="down" data-layer-type="${type}" data-layer-index="${index}" aria-label="Move down">${icon('caret-down')}</button>`:''}</div></div>`;
    const group=(title,body)=>`<section class="dp-editor-sidebar-group"><h3>${escapeHtml(title)}</h3>${body}</section>`;
    const renderSidebar=()=>{
        const sidebarPanel=sidebar.closest('.dp-editor-sidebar');
        const previousScroll=sidebarPanel?.scrollTop||0;
        document.getElementById('dp-editor-sidebar-title').textContent=pageLabels[page];
        let html='';
        if(page==='shop'){
            html+=group('Header',layerButton('header','Store header','navigation',null,{icon:'nav-store'})+layerButton('announcement','Announcement bar','promotion',null,{icon:'info'}));
            html+=group('Sections',layerButton('hero','Hero carousel',`${slides.length} slide${slides.length===1?'':'s'}`,null,{icon:'nav-dashboard'})+slides.map((slide,index)=>layerButton('slide',`${index+1}. ${slide.headline||'Untitled slide'}`,'hero slide',index,{draggable:true,visibility:true,visible:slide.visible})).join('')+`<button type="button" class="dp-editor-add-button dp-editor-add-block" data-add-kind="slide">${icon('actions-add')}Add hero slide</button>`+layerButton('catalog','Product catalog',`${products.length} product${products.length===1?'':'s'}`,null,{icon:'nav-products'})+categories.map((category,index)=>layerButton('category',category.name||`Category ${index+1}`,'category',index,{draggable:true,visibility:true,visible:category.visible})).join('')+`<button type="button" class="dp-editor-add-button dp-editor-add-block" data-add-kind="category">${icon('actions-add')}Add category</button>`);
            html+=group('Footer',layerButton('footer','Store footer','links and attribution',null,{icon:'nav-menu'}));
        }else{
            html+=group('Page content',layerButton(page,pageLabels[page],page==='product'?'commerce page':'customer page',null,{icon:page==='login'?'lock':page==='payment'?'checkout-sent':page==='success'?'checkout-complete':page==='product'||page==='library'?'nav-products':'pos-cart'}));
            html+=group('Shared layout',layerButton('header','Store header','navigation',null,{icon:'nav-store'})+layerButton('footer','Store footer','links and attribution',null,{icon:'nav-menu'}));
        }
        html+=group('General settings',layerButton('general','Theme & styles','colors and typography',null,{icon:'themes-light'})+layerButton('experience','Customer experience','access and emails',null,{icon:'nav-account'}));
        sidebar.innerHTML=html;
        if(sidebarPanel)sidebarPanel.scrollTop=previousScroll;
        updateTopbar();
    };

    const field=(label,id,type='text',help='',attrs='')=>`<label for="builder-${id}">${escapeHtml(label)}</label>${type==='textarea'?`<textarea id="builder-${id}" rows="4" data-bind-target="${id}" ${attrs}>${escapeHtml(value(id))}</textarea>`:type==='select'?`<select id="builder-${id}" data-bind-target="${id}" ${attrs}>${help}</select>`:`<input id="builder-${id}" type="${type}" value="${escapeAttribute(value(id))}" data-bind-target="${id}" ${attrs}>`}${type!=='select'&&help?`<p class="dp-editor-help">${escapeHtml(help)}</p>`:''}`;
    const section=(title,body,action='')=>`<section class="dp-editor-inspector-section"><div class="dp-editor-section-head"><h3>${escapeHtml(title)}</h3>${action}</div>${body}</section>`;
    const check=(label,attribute,checked)=>`<label class="dp-editor-check"><input type="checkbox" ${attribute} ${checked?'checked':''}> ${escapeHtml(label)}</label>`;
    const productOptions=selectedValue=>`<option value="">No attached product</option>${products.map(product=>`<option value="${escapeAttribute(product.reference)}" ${product.reference===selectedValue?'selected':''}>${escapeHtml(product.name)} · ${escapeHtml(product.kind)}</option>`).join('')}`;
    const renderInspector=(preserveScroll=true)=>{
        const inspectorPanel=inspector.closest('.dp-editor-inspector');
        const previousScroll=inspectorPanel?.scrollTop||0;
        let html='';
        let title='Section settings';
        if(selected.type==='header'){
            title='Header';
